Papers
======

Working papers by David Walther.
Source in Markdown. Published as PDF, DOCX, and Markdown.

Contents
--------

  12hz-power-grid  12 Hz power grid architecture
  entfesselt       Entfesselt — liberating Germanic from Latin grammar

Build
-----

  make              Build all PDFs and DOCX files
  make pdf          PDFs only
  make docx         DOCX only
  make publish      Build + commit + push

Output lands in dist/.

Paper format
------------

Each paper.md begins with:

  ---
  title: "Title"
  author: "David Walther"
  date: "2026"
  abstract: |
    One-paragraph summary.
  ---

Requirements: pandoc, xelatex (TeX Live)

  sudo apt install pandoc texlive-xetex texlive-fonts-recommended
